arger radius either since birth, or get it after a\nviolent interaction with the galactic center. The diversity of environments\nacross space and time in a galaxy merger can account for the diversity of the\nstellar objects formed, both in terms of mass and size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Oct 2014 17:40:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
