ere the dynamics is monotone. These results apply both\nto the optimal selection of equilibria and periodic solutions, as well as to\nfinite-horizon network trajectory optimization.\n  Finally, we illustrate our findings through simulations on a road network\ninspired by the freeway system in southern Los Angeles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Oct 2014 09:13:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Oct 2014 09:41:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-28"}
